This paper is about using deep neural networks for facial image analysis tasks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of synthetic face images for pre-training the networks, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the generation of 3D models, which could be categorized under computer graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
